headers.subject: [tosdr:958] Square TOS

html:
Square says it can change it's fees at any time, but it will provide 30 days notice to users beforehand.
They reserve the right, but say they are not obliged to delete all account information if the account is terminated.
At any time, Square can terminate your account for any reason or no reason with notice to you.
https://squareup.com/legal/merchant-ua

Square will not notify users it has changed its privacy policy except by posting a new version and updating the last updated date:
https://squareup.com/legal/privacy
